{"_path":"/councilor/service/s3020","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"增設YouBike 站點","description":null,"image":"/images/service/s3020-1.jpeg","sequence":3020,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/16GbK8TVG2/","author":"孫韻璇","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"孫韻璇"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-05-10T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"增設-youbike-站點"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"增設 YouBike 站點"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最近韻璇最常聽到的，就是鄉親對 YouBike 的反映。\n不論是上班通勤、接送小孩，還是到市場買菜，交通便利與否，真的深深影響著我們的生活品質。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這次我實地 #會勘了兩個龜山地點，回應大家 #希望增設 YouBike 站 的心聲："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n在 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"#鴻築金捷市"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，我們原本希望能增設柱位，但礙於現地空間有限，暫時無法設站。我知道這讓人有點失望，但我們沒放棄，而是請微笑單車增派調度車輛，讓車位流動更順，減少大家借不到、還不了的困擾。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"至於 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"#牛角坡樂善一路"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，原有 20 根停車柱，經過現勘確認可望增設 30 根柱位，升級為約 50 柱大站，讓上下坡的民眾在使用上更輕鬆、更便利！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我們龜山幅員廣、起伏多，YouBike 不只是單車，更是生活中重要的一環。我會繼續努力，讓公共運輸越來越貼近大家的需求。謝謝你們一路上的反映與支持，有你們的聲音，我就有前進的方向。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"#為地方 #我們一起努力"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s3020-01.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s3020-01.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"增設-youbike-站點","depth":2,"text":"增設 YouBike 站點"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s3020.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s3020.md","_extension":"md"}